                              xmi:type="uml:Association">
               <ownedComment xmi:id="ddsc.InstanceVariable_takesSubstantiveValuesFrom_SubstantiveValueDomain-ownedComment"
                              xmi:uuid="http://w3id.org/cdif/ddsc/1.0/ddsc/xmi/#InstanceVariable_takesSubstantiveValuesFrom_SubstantiveValueDomain-ownedComment"
                              xmi:type="uml:Comment">
                  <body>The substantive representation (substantive value domain) of the variable. This is equivalent to the relationship "Measures" in the Generic Statistical Information Model (GSIM) although GSIM makes no distinction between substantive and sentinel values.</body>
