                                 xmi:uuid="http://w3id.org/cdif/ddsc/1.0/ddsc/xmi/#RepresentedVariable-describedUnitOfMeasure-ownedComment"
                                 xmi:type="uml:Comment">
                     <body>The unit in which the data values are measured (kg, pound, euro), expressed as a value from a controlled system of entries (i.e., QDT). Supports the provision of an identifier for the entry in the authoritative source (a URI, etc.), and the specific vocabulary.</body>
